This is an auxiliary template to standardize colors used in [[Metro-North Railroad]] articles and templates.

=== Usage ===
In order to call a line's colour, the code <code> #&#123;&#123;MNRR color|<i>name</i>}}</code>  is used (where ''name'' is replaced by the actual route name or abbreviation). Note that this template is not case sensitive: i.e. <code><nowiki>{{MNRR color|NH}}</nowiki></code> produces the same result as <code><nowiki>{{MNRR color|nh}}</nowiki></code>.

